scenes.description: Amelia shows the birthday merch message card and mentions some audio static issues.
Transitioning from the merch slideshow to a new intro screen.
Amelia introduces an interactive pixel-art claw machine game for the chat.
Amelia starts a recap list on-screen and talks about her recent trip to Japan.
